Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with Obelisk's greatest Ability,\N Soul Energy Max, I couldn't defeat Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I still have the servants who fought hard for me in the Battle City tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll borrow all of their power,\N as I activate the Magic Card, Ragnarok!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, I shall use this to destroy you and Ra fused as a Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End of Battle City!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were still alive, Rishid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty damn {\i1}tough{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, even if you've shown your ass after all this time,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be switching\N personalities anytime {\i1}soon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ri...shid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Rishid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even walk straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is Rishid's only wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a vile carving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it no longer holds any {\i1}meaning{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dominant self's psyche is like that\N of a candle flame in the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even have the strength\N to {\i1}speak{\i0}, let alone to {\i1}live{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cruel fate of the Tomb Guardians\N is what brought this tragedy upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resentment towards the Ishtar clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anger and hatred lying dormant\N within you is what created the\N evil heart that stands before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SHUT UP ALREADY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, you {\b0}bastard{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are about to throw yourself\N into the darkness of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... alright....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, even if your path leads into\N darkness, you must continue living!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not just\N the fate of a Tomb Guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the fate of {\i1}every{\i0} human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fate... of every human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I TOLD YOU\N TO SHUT THE HELL UP-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not through {\i1}death{\i0}\N that people go into the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is light only in {\i1}life{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have this much\N strength left in you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence...! Get {\i1}lost{\i0}, you leech...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've committed\N an unforgivable crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crime so bad, a Tomb Guardian like\N myself cannot be forgiven for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my hatred for the Pharaoh\N that led to the Ishtar tragedy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And created my other self...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told\N you to be {\i1}silent{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it's because of my dark heart\N that this evil monster was created!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all that, do you think someone\N like myself can head towards the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP! SHUT {\i1}UP{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some way I can put an end to\N this never ending sorrow and hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'll find out\N in your next attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SILENCE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me, Malik's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's betting everything\N on this one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel his strong spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in your strength,\N your one point of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate my reverse Magic,\N Ragnarok! Final Destiny of the Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnarok is a Magic Card that can only be\N activated when both Black Magician and\N Black Magician Girl are on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its effect allows me to remove from play\N every Monster in my deck,\N my hand, and my Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, it destroys every\N Monster of the opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop.... it....!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the target is a {\i1}god{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk is here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s\N Monsters are appearing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LET ME GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Burning Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Yugi win?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik still has 1 remaining Life Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other me believed that Malik\N had the strength to live\N on one Life Point...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik's expression changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is his dark personality gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik, you had the strength to live\N within your heart this entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that strength has overcome\N your evil heart and your evil half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... I still have\N 1 Life Point remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel is not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the {\i1}hell{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik and his dominant personality\N switched places! Now {\i1}he's{\i0} the sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}can't{\i0} be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way my half-dead\N dominant half had enough\N will power to overtake me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take over the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop {\i1}joking{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a sacrifice\N because of just {\i1}one{\i0} point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dominant Half!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought of us\N as {\i1}friends{\i0} sharing the same body!\N We're the {\i1}same{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a chance we can\N {\i1}win{\i0} this Duel, even with {\i1}one{\i0} Life Point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because of {\i1}him{\i0}\N that you suffered the terrible\N fate of the Tomb Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get revenge for\N you and your ancestors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the dark side I created,\N spawned by my suffering as a\N result of that very same fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer\N control my subconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0}....?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy you\N with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Madness...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he planning to give up his body\N in order to destroy me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crimes I committed\N will never be cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will live, bearing my guilt like\N these carvings on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like to chase\N the light of hope once again amidst\N the darkness of my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, soul of the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for\N saving me in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You {\i1}wouldn't{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terrible fate of the Ishtar\N clan lasting 3,000 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tragedy caused by me\N shutting myself in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must put an end to it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All with these hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will at least be some atonement\N for the sin I've committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the first step...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...into the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He surrendered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He conceded defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Life Points automatically\N dropped to 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sur..... rend..... dered....?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IMPOSSIBLE...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dark self!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost everything, Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik... Our future was not lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik, you were victorious in\N the Duel against your {\i1}heart{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle City Finals are over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALRIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}YUGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To all my cards\N who lent me strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And... my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sister... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For thousands of years,\N our family has suffered a cruel fate\N as we lived in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was {\i1}your{\i0} destiny to end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishly pursuing revenge only\N leads to further tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we, the Ishtars,\N were assigned the duty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of guarding\N the Pharaoh's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so our Pharaoh could\N {\i1}teach{\i0} us that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, do you think our family\N can escape the chains of darkness and live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us, after all, are not just\N of the same tribe, but {\i1}family{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we hold this bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can endure any obstacle\N we may face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this very moment,\N by winning Battle City, you have just\N earned the title of Duel King!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the host of this tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I applaud your achievement!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I hadn't taken the card you gave me,\N I wouldn't have been able to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the winner, Yugi,\N you get to take Malik's Ante Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time to fulfill your\N final duty as a Tomb Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark spells placed\N on your friends who lost to me\N in the Dark Games have been lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll regain consciousness soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And {\b0}me{\b1} too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, here's the God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Osiris the Heaven Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great War God Obelisk...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, the three God Cards\N are in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those three cards hold the secret\N of the other me's memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key to the Pharaoh's memories,\N which the Tomb Guardian clan\N has protected for centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It lies right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful that\N must have been...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This cruel scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is {\b0}this{\b1} how the Tomb Guardians\N guarded my memory for\N so many generations...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These hieroglyphs contain a prophecized\N message passed down from the first Tomb\N Guardian who served under the Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:16:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the future, one will come\N who will wield the power of the\N three gods depicted on the stone slab."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This will be proof that the\N Pharaoh's soul has been reincarnated."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, since you now hold the three God Cards, it is proof that you are the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, you deserve to know the\N {\i1}truth{\i0} of your long-lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words of this ancient language\N hold no meaning to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's like the three God Cards\N are sending a vision through me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That slate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is my memory truly sealed\N within that slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my mission has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take my Millennium Rod,\N one of the Millennium Items my tribe\N risked their lives to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Millennium Ring as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished\N soaking in all the glory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle City Tournament\N has now officially ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I will lend you my pride and\N the title of Duel King for the time being!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final location of \Nthe Battle City Finals, the Duel Tower,\N has now outlived its usefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, in exactly one hour\N from now, this structure will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WH-WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Kaiba!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of you will be\N evacuated aboard the Battle Ship and\N escorted off of Alcatraz Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't the engine\N in the Battle Ship damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that!\N Repairs finished a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Isono?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! We can't just stand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to being a sore loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! What's Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations are all okay, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with this, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inputting password code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inputting... complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye, ghost of Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1... 2... and 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Self-Detonation procedure launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One hour remaining until explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please hurry! Get aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka, how's Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, how could something\N this stupid happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die...! Don't die, MAI!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DON'T DIE!! MAI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, were you {\i1}crying{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were {\i1}that{\i0} worried about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you {\i1}bitch{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were {\i1}fooling{\i0} me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0},\N it went just as I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so simple-minded, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, we were so worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that leaves Bakura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you guys! Thank goodness\N I finally found you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}our{\i0} line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell {\i1}were{\i0} you up 'till now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really {\i1}know{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, I was lying in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did ya know, I was {\i1}starving{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?! Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0} and\N Mokuba-{\i1}sama{\i0} aren't back yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could they have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't on the Battle Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is Kaiba doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's going to\N kill himself because he can't\N accept his loss to Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no {\i1}way{\i0} that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the {\i1}same guy{\i0} we're talking about,\N don't you think he escaped already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, what if you're wrong...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we can't just leave them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped... let's go look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you guys prepare for our escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that guy\N causes a lot of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compressor running!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voltage is good! Fuel is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine... stopped...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said it was {\i1}fixed{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}45 minutes remaining until explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After setting up the explosion for the island, Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} and Mokuba-{\i0}kun{\i1} just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can it be those two plan to sink with the island and bury themselves at sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to top it off, the Battle Ship's engine stopped working again, so we have no way off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have to hurry and find those two, since there's no time left 'till the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}, Mokuba-{\i0}kun{\i1}! Where in the world {\b0}are{\b1} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alcatraz Burns"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:23:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
